      "value": "\r\n<p class=\"source\"><b>Source</b> <em>PZO1115</em></p>\r\n<p>This flask of caustic liquid reacts with an <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/bestiary/rules-for-monsters/creature-types#TOC-Ooze\">ooze's</a> <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/glossary#TOC-Bonus-Natural-Armor-\">natural</a> acids. You can throw an alkali flask as a <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Throw-Splash-Weapon\">splash weapon</a> with a range increment of 10 feet. Against non-ooze creatures, an alkali flask functions as a normal flask of acid. Against <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/bestiary/rules-for-monsters/creature-types#TOC-Ooze\">oozes</a> and other acid-based creatures, the alkali flask inflicts double damage.</p>\r\n<p><b>Create</b>: <a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/craft\">Craft</a> (alchemy) DC 20</p>\r\n"
